new
domain extent -1 1

wall generate box 0 0.85 0 0.85


ball distribute porosity 0.12 radius 3e-3 5e-3 box 0 0.85 0 0.85
ball attribute density 1800
ball attribute damp 0.1
cmat default model linear property kn 1e9 ks 1e9 fric 0.1

set timestep scale

cycle 1000 calm 50

set timestep auto
cycle 1000
solve aratio 1e-4
save sample